## 14. Distribution Shapes

## Approximately Symmetrical

```text
Frequency
   |
   |       ***
   |     *******
   |   ***********
   |________________
             Values
```

Values are distributed similarly around the center.

## Right-Skewed

```text
Frequency
   |
   | ****
   | ******
   |   ****
   |      ***______
   |________________
             Values
```

Most values are lower, with a long tail toward higher values.

## Left-Skewed

```text
Frequency
   |
   |       ****
   |     ******
   |   ****
   |___**
   |________________
             Values
```

Most values are higher, with a long tail toward lower values.

